## Preparing for Physical Prototyping

##### When students are building physical prototypes, they will access to materials to build with. You might consider having some of the following available for students to work with: 

* ##### Structural material (cardboard, construction paper, etc)
* ##### Connective material (tape, glue, hot glue, etc)
* ##### Construction tools (scissors, staplers, etc)
* ##### Other materials (cups, binder clips, paper plates, etc)

##### **Tip:** Consider what physical materials are worth collecting and stockpiling ahead of time to prepare for this project


